# Exports

- **No default exports** — always use named exports
- `index.ts` files are for re-exports only — no logic, no component definitions

```ts
// ❌
export default function UserCard() {}

// ✅
export function UserCard() {}
```

```ts
// ❌ index.ts with logic
export function buildUrl(path: string) { ... }

// ✅ index.ts re-exports only
export { buildUrl } from './build-url'
export { parseQuery } from './parse-query'
```

Config files (`vite.config.ts`, etc.) are exempt — they require default exports by convention.
